title: Iron Man 2.0 (2011-2012, Complete)
description: Collects all 12 main issues of Iron Man 2.0, as well as issue 7.1. Written by Nick Spencer with art by Barry Kitson. Spins directly out of Matt Fraction's run on Invincible Iron Man, and the storyline focuses on War Machine dealing with enemies in ways he is not used to. Published by Marvel, all credit to original scanners. Please seed, and enjoy! :-)
